Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 743 Filed 08/10/22 Page 193 of 247 321 LBUVMAX4 Jane - direct

1 A. My eyes didn't even look at the walls, mostly the floor, if not what was going on.
2
3 Q. Was there any other furniture inside the massage room aside from the massage table?
4
5 A. I don't know.
6
7 Q. Earlier you testified that you recall traveling to New Mexico; is that correct?
8
9 A. Yes.
10
11 Q. Approximately when did you travel to New Mexico?
12
13 A. The year?
14
15 Q. Approximately how old were you when you traveled to New Mexico?
16
17 A. Oh, 15 or 16.
18
19 Q. Who went with you on that trip?
20
21 A. Jeffrey and Ghislaine.
22
23 Q. Where did you spend most of your time on the trip to New Mexico with Maxwell and Epstein?
24
25 A. At Epstein's house, which was a ranch.
26
27 Q. What do you remember about the ranch that you visited on that trip?
28
29 A. I just remember that it was this giant ranch sort of in the middle of nowhere. And it seemed very empty on the interior, meaning there wasn't really any other people around.
30
31 Q. When you were at the ranch in New Mexico, where did you spend most of your time?

SOUTHERN DISTRICT REPORTERS, P.C. (212) 805-0300

DOJ-OGR-00011965
